{"tid":831602,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"懵仔針主要成分係氟化物，食水又加咗氟，咁飲得水多會唔會等於打咗懵仔針一次？","createTime":"2018-09-22T05:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T13:54:42.000Z","uid":20816,"like":6,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"ac8a8a618df853e7fa6c3245fbeea56bfc06db3a","tid":831602,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"氟哌啶醇（Haloperidol），是一種典型抗精神疾病藥物（英語：Typical antipsychotic）[3]。該藥可用於治療思覺失調症、妥瑞氏症的抽動、噁心、嘔吐、譫妄、躁動、思覺失調，以及戒酒症狀[3][4]。氟哌啶醇可透過口服、肌肉注射、靜脈注射等方法給藥。藥物約會於30-60分鐘後開始作用。精神分裂症及相關疾病患者如果會忘記或拒絕服藥，可每四週注射一次長效配方[3]。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/氟哌啶醇\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%B0%9F%E5%93%8C%E5%95%B6%E9%86%87&d=v8KQLTnareU90bbLtfNQZEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7a4176b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/氟哌啶醇</a>"},{"pid":"8472182bf86e1e38c5b2c9792dda0eb3f2750c3b","tid":831602,"uid":3581,"like":84,"dislike":2,"score":82,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"懵仔針主要成分係水"},{"pid":"bf520377cc2ecc7cf02ec84a757c02ed517b564b","tid":831602,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"8472182bf86e1e38c5b2c9792dda0eb3f2750c3b","tid":831602,"uid":3581,"like":84,"dislike":2,"score":82,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"懵仔針主要成分係水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ae8c5325b2c90a55b55c85f10265c477ff1b27","tid":831602,"uid":39722,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"8472182bf86e1e38c5b2c9792dda0eb3f2750c3b","tid":831602,"uid":3581,"like":84,"dislike":2,"score":82,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"懵仔針主要成分係水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:57:06.000Z","msg":"飲得水多會變樓豬咁"},{"pid":"f28864558853b1274681b01a781e28e22250aca0","tid":831602,"uid":20816,"like":8,"dislike":43,"score":-35,"quote":{"pid":"13ae8c5325b2c90a55b55c8